<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1949-06-28T07:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1949-06-28T07:00:00-05:00" n="964" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d964">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">893.6363/6–2849: Telegram</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in the United Kingdom</hi> (<persName type="from"><hi rend="italic">Douglas</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                            </hi>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">London</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1949-06-28T13:00:00+01:00">June 28,
                                    1949—1 p. m.</date>
                                <lb/> [Received 2:35 p. m.]</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>2485. Embtel 2470, June 27. Foreign Office informs Embassy they agree
                            with US position and have instructed Anglo-Iranian not to accept long
                            term contract supply petroleum to China though they are, of course, free
                            compete if they wish on basis which would permit termination of supplies
                            on short notice.</p>
                        <p>In addition, UK has instructed oil companies not to sell aviation
                            gasoline to Formosa as long as Nationalistic Chinese embargo shipping
                            Communist China is in effect.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Douglas</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>